    Online ordering for pick-up and delivery is available until 30 minutes before closing. Please call 917-261-7005 to place an order if online ordering is unavailable (pick-up only). Orders placed on this page are for the 80 Maiden Lane location. Requests for extra ingredients in the "special requests" section may be subject to extra charge (condiments and seasonings are free). If you would like to request additional ingredients for a dish, we recommend placing a phone or in-person order.
